<D>__{i said stop!}
<A>__{the robot. suddenly swinging the suitcase around. smashing it against spooner's head. spooner. buckles. falling to the ground. managing to squeeze off a shot... the robot. deflecting the bullet. with the case. raising it as if to club spooner with it when... bam! spooner fires a second shot. piercing the robot's breastplate. hydraulic fluid. starting to leak. the robot. doesn't hesitate. slams the case into spooner's face... blood. spurting from spooner's nose. as he fires the gun. at the fleeing robot. gets to his feet. unsteady. taking chase...}
